{"title":"Quick Start : Lacework","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"### Quick Start : Lacework

Lacework is a SaaS platform that provides automated threat defense, intrusion detection, and compliance for multicloud workloads & containers.

BridgeCrew deployed Lacework's AWS Compliance module to provide insights into existing violations. Lacework will monitor and alert any time a configuration goes out of compliance.
